- `n == online.length`
- `2 <= n <= 5 * 104`
- `0 <= m == edges.length <= min(105, n * (n - 1) / 2)`
- `edges[i] = [ui, vi, costi]`
- `0 <= ui, vi < n`
- `ui != vi`
- `0 <= costi <= 109`
- `0 <= k <= 5 * 1013`
